ssh s3it # log in to the cluster (e.g. hydra, vesta, etc.)
q # bashrc-defined shortcut to view status of jobs
module avail # all available modules
module list # all loaded modules
module purge # purge all modules or specify one

squeue # check how far along your script is in the slurm queue

sbatch run_dmrg # run the script for run_dmrg

Example Slurm Batch Scripts: https://www.id.uzh.ch/en/scienceit/infrastructure/usage/examples.html

